{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/banner.png?t=1718417603\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/outpt.gif?t=1718417603\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/separator.png?t=1718417603\" /><br><br>Congratulations!<br><br>You have secured a job at the food distribution center in the state of Nowhere! A country where the new authorities seek to subjugate the population under their control, heavily restricting access to food.<br><br>In your role as employee 100411, you will process customers' food purchases at your station. Controlling, through the mechanisms provided by the state, that the customer's documentation and the products they buy are valid.<br><br>But BEWARE! Forgers, alcoholics, robbers, thieves, wanted criminals, drug addicts, the poor \u2013 all of them will seek, by any means, to access the food. Your task will be to keep them at bay. ARREST civilians, become a subject to the regime, or REBEL... But ALL decisions have consequences.<br><br>Will you enforce the prohibitions while the poor starve? Or will you let them tug at your heartstrings and turn a blind eye?<br><br>And remember, under the new food reorganization program, you must strictly adhere to regulations, lest you suffer the consequences. The state of Nowhere does not tolerate sentimentality.<br><br>All those employees who serve the state exceptionally will be blessed by our honorable president, Maligno.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/sello.png?t=1718417603\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/separator.png?t=1718417603\" /><br><br>&quot;The State of Nowhere&quot; is a casual single-player simulation game set in a totalitarian state, where you take on the role of a state employee responsible for providing food to the citizens. It will be your responsibility to control and decide who will be able to receive their food. This will require you to perform a variety of tasks, including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Analyzing the validity of the presented documentation<br></li><li>    Conducting different types of scans on clients for irregularities<br></li><li>    Checking food restrictions<br></li><li>    Processing payment for the food</li></ul><br>The game will initially be available in English and Spanish, but we plan to add more languages in the future, such as Portuguese, French, Chinese, Japanese, Russian, Korean, Italian and German, among others.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/separator.png?t=1718417603\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1718417603","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1718417603","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1718417603","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1718417603","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/banner.png?t=1718417603\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/outpt.gif?t=1718417603\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799170/extras/separator.png?t=1718417603\" /><br>